name: ChartData
func:
var dataArray = msg.payload.split(',')
var m = {};

m.labels = ['0',
        '45',
        '90',
        '135',
        '180',
        '225',
        '270',
        '315'];
m.data = [dataArray];
m.series = [
        '0',
        '45',
        '90',
        '135',
        '180',
        '225',
        '270',
        '315'];
return {payload:[m],topic:msg.topic};
